title: 121: Week 3 Review & Undrafted with Jeremiah Allison
itunes:title: 121: Week 3 Review & Undrafted with Jeremiah Allison
description:
Former NFL scouts Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks review the top performances from defenses and rookie quarterbacks thus far this season. The guys are then joined by Jeremiah Allison, one of the stars of the NFL Network show Undrafted, to talk about his journey from high school in Los Angeles, to college at Washington State, before chasing the NFL dream.
